snippet.title: Amber Heard WANTS Harry Potter Role After Johnny Depp's Gone
snippet.description:
Amber Heard WANTS Harry Potter Role After Johnny Depp's Gone
Latest rumors are that Heard is trying to get herself a role somewhere in the Harry Potter franchise. Will she get the role despite her already damaged reputation?
Stick around to find out. And also give this video a thumbs up as I tell you more about this development.
Sources say that the Aquaman actress is looking to strengthen her relationship with Warner Bros by landing a gig in the franchise that formerly featured her ex-husband, Johnny Depp.
